drop table "MD_Category" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "MD_Category" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "MD_Category"
(
"CategoryID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"REMCategoryGUID" VARCHAR2(100),
"CategoryName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"CategoryCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"CategoryLevel" INTEGER not null,
"ParentID" NUMBER(32),
"OrderNum" NUMBER(10) not null,
"Remark" NVARCHAR2(500),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_MD_CATEGORY primary key ("CategoryID")
);

comment on column "MD_Category"."CategoryLevel" is
'1:大类、
2:一级分类
3:二级分类';

comment on column "MD_Category"."OrderNum" is
'父品类下面的子品类排序';

comment on column "MD_Category"."Enable" is
'1: 有效
0：无效';
